Get the result of the work item. If the work item didn't run yet then the caller waits until timeout or until the cancelWaitHandle is signaled.

exitContext true to exit the synchronization domain for the context before the wait (if in a synchronized context), and reacquire it; otherwise, false.
cancelWaitHandle A cancel wait handle to interrupt the blocking if needed
